{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Just to put everything in context,"},{"time":2000,"text":"and to kind of give you a background to where I'm coming from,"},{"time":6000,"text":"so that a lot of the things I'm going to say,"},{"time":8000,"text":"and the things I'm going to do --"},{"time":11000,"text":"or things I'm going to tell you I've done --"},{"time":13000,"text":"you will understand exactly why and how I got motivated to be where I am."},{"time":20000,"text":"I graduated high school in Cleveland, Ohio, 1975."},{"time":24000,"text":"And just like my parents did when they finished studying abroad, we went back home."},{"time":30000,"text":"Finished university education, got a medical degree, 1986."},{"time":35000,"text":"And by the time I was an intern house officer,"},{"time":39000,"text":"I could barely afford to maintain my mother's 13-year-old car --"},{"time":44000,"text":"and I was a paid doctor."},{"time":48000,"text":"This brings us to why a lot of us, who are professionals,"},{"time":52000,"text":"are now, as they say, in diaspora."},{"time":56000,"text":"Now, are we going to make that a permanent thing,"},{"time":59000,"text":"where we all get trained, and we leave, and we don't go back?"},{"time":66000,"text":"Perhaps not, I should certainly hope not --"},{"time":69000,"text":"because that is not my vision."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73000,"text":"All right, for good measure, that's where Nigeria is on the African map,"},{"time":79000,"text":"and just there is the Delta region that I'm sure everybody's heard of."},{"time":84000,"text":"People getting kidnapped, where the oil comes from,"},{"time":88000,"text":"the oil that sometimes I think has driven us all crazy in Nigeria."},{"time":93000,"text":"But, critical poverty: this slide is from a presentation I gave"},{"time":96000,"text":"not that long ago. Gapminder.org tells the story of the gap"},{"time":102000,"text":"between Africa and the rest of the world in terms of health care."},{"time":106000,"text":"Very interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"How many people do you think are on that taxi?"},{"time":113000,"text":"And believe it or not, that is a taxi in Nigeria."},{"time":116000,"text":"And the capital -- well, what used to be the capital of Nigeria -- Lagos,"},{"time":119000,"text":"that's a taxi, and you have police on them."},{"time":122000,"text":"So, tell me, how many policemen do you think are on this taxi? And now? Three."},{"time":130000,"text":"So, when these kind of people -- and, believe me, it's not just the police"},{"time":135000,"text":"that use these taxis in Lagos. We all do. I've been on one of these,"},{"time":140000,"text":"and I didn't have a helmet, either."},{"time":143000,"text":"And it just reminds me of the thought of what happens when one of us"},{"time":151000,"text":"on a taxi like this falls off, has an accident and needs a hospital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157000,"text":"Believe it or not, some of us do survive."},{"time":161000,"text":"Some of us do survive malaria; we do survive AIDS."},{"time":165000,"text":"And like I tell my family, and my wife reminds me every time,"},{"time":169000,"text":"\"You're risking your life, you know, every time you go to that country.\""},{"time":173000,"text":"And she's right. Every time you go there,"},{"time":176000,"text":"you know that if you actually need critical care --"},{"time":181000,"text":"critical care of any sort -- if you have an accident --"},{"time":184000,"text":"of which there are many, there are accidents everywhere --"},{"time":188000,"text":"where do they go?"},{"time":191000,"text":"Where do they go when they need help for this kind of stuff?"},{"time":196000,"text":"I'm not saying instead of, I'm saying as well as,"},{"time":199000,"text":"AIDS, TB, malaria, typhoid -- the list goes on."},{"time":205000,"text":"I'm saying, where do they go when they're like me?"},{"time":209000,"text":"When I go back home -- and I do all kinds of things,"},{"time":212000,"text":"I teach, I train -- but I catch one of these things,"},{"time":216000,"text":"or I'm chronically ill with one of those, where do they go?"},{"time":222000,"text":"What's the economic impact when one of them dies or becomes disabled?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"I think it's quite significant. This is where they go."},{"time":232000,"text":"These are not old pictures and these are not from some downtrodden --"},{"time":236000,"text":"this is a major hospital. In fact, it's from a major teaching hospital in Nigeria."},{"time":242000,"text":"Now that is less than a year old, in an operating room."},{"time":247000,"text":"That's sterilizing equipment in Nigeria."},{"time":250000,"text":"You remember all that oil?"},{"time":252000,"text":"Yes, I'm sorry if it upsets some of you, but"},{"time":256000,"text":"I think you need to see this. That's the floor, OK?"},{"time":260000,"text":"You can say some of this is education."},{"time":262000,"text":"You can say it's hygiene. I'm not pleading poverty."},{"time":266000,"text":"I'm saying we need more than just, you know, vaccination,"},{"time":272000,"text":"malaria, AIDS, because I want to be treated"},{"time":275000,"text":"in a proper hospital if something happens to me out there."},{"time":278000,"text":"In fact, when I start running around saying,"},{"time":280000,"text":"\"Hey, boys and girls, you're cardiologists in the U.S.,"},{"time":283000,"text":"can you come home with me and do a mission?\""},{"time":286000,"text":"I want them to think, \"Well there's some hope.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":288000,"text":"Now, have a look at that. That's the anesthesiology machine."},{"time":291000,"text":"And that's my specialty, right?"},{"time":293000,"text":"Anesthesiology and critical care -- look at that bag."},{"time":297000,"text":"It's been taped with tape that we even stopped using in the U.K."},{"time":301000,"text":"And believe me, these are current pictures."},{"time":304000,"text":"Now, if something like this, which has happened in the U.K.,"},{"time":309000,"text":"that's where they go. This is the intensive care unit in which I work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314000,"text":"All right, this is a slide from a talk I gave"},{"time":319000,"text":"about intensive care units in Nigeria,"},{"time":323000,"text":"and jokingly we refer to it as \"Expensive Scare.\""},{"time":328000,"text":"Because it's scary and it's expensive, but we need to have it, OK?"},{"time":336000,"text":"So, these are the problems."},{"time":339000,"text":"There are no prizes for telling us what the problems are, are there?"},{"time":343000,"text":"I think we all know. And several speakers before"},{"time":346000,"text":"and speakers after me are going to tell us even more problems."},{"time":350000,"text":"These are a few of them. So, what did I do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":354000,"text":"There we go -- we're going on a mission."},{"time":357000,"text":"We're going to do some open-heart surgery. I was the only Brit,"},{"time":361000,"text":"on a team of about nine American cardiac surgeons,"},{"time":366000,"text":"cardiac nurse, intensive care nurse."},{"time":368000,"text":"We all went out and did a mission and we've done three of them so far."},{"time":373000,"text":"Just so you know, I do believe in missions, I do believe in aid"},{"time":377000,"text":"and I do believe in charity. They have their place,"},{"time":380000,"text":"but where do they go for those things we talked about earlier?"},{"time":385000,"text":"Because it's not everyone that's going to benefit from a mission."},{"time":390000,"text":"Health is wealth, in the words of Hans Rosling."},{"time":393000,"text":"You get wealthier faster if you are healthy first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399000,"text":"So, here we are, mission. Big trouble."},{"time":403000,"text":"Open-heart surgery in Nigeria -- big trouble."},{"time":406000,"text":"That's Mike, Mike comes out from Mississippi."},{"time":409000,"text":"Does he look like he's happy?"},{"time":411000,"text":"It took us two days just to organize the place, but hey,"},{"time":415000,"text":"you know, we worked on it. Does he look happy?"},{"time":420000,"text":"Yes, that's the medical advice the committee chairman says,"},{"time":422000,"text":"\"Yes, I told you, you weren't going to be able to,"},{"time":424000,"text":"you can't do this, I just know it.\""},{"time":426000,"text":"Look, that's the technician we had. So yes, you go on, all right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":432000,"text":"I got him to come with me -- anesthesia tech -- come with me from the U.K."},{"time":436000,"text":"Yes, let's just go work this thing out."},{"time":440000,"text":"See, that's one of the problems we have in Nigeria and in Africa generally."},{"time":444000,"text":"We get a lot of donated equipment."},{"time":446000,"text":"Equipment that's obsolete, equipment that doesn't quite work,"},{"time":449000,"text":"or it works and you can't fix it. And there's nothing wrong with that,"},{"time":453000,"text":"so long as we use it and we move on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456000,"text":"But we had problems with it. We had severe problems there."},{"time":458000,"text":"He had to get on the phone. This guy was always on the phone."},{"time":461000,"text":"So what we going to do now?"},{"time":463000,"text":"It looks like all these Americans are here and"},{"time":465000,"text":"yes, one Brit, and he's not going to do anything --"},{"time":469000,"text":"he thinks he's British actually, and he's actually Nigerian,"},{"time":471000,"text":"I just thought about that."},{"time":473000,"text":"We eventually got it working, is the truth,"},{"time":475000,"text":"but it was one of these. Even older than the one you saw."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479000,"text":"The reason I have this picture here, this X-ray,"},{"time":482000,"text":"it's just to tell you where and how we were viewing X-rays."},{"time":488000,"text":"Do you figure where that is? It was on a window."},{"time":491000,"text":"I mean, what's an X-ray viewing box? Please."},{"time":496000,"text":"Well, nowadays everything's on PAX anyway."},{"time":499000,"text":"You look at your X-rays on a screen and you do stuff with them,"},{"time":503000,"text":"you email them. But we were still using X-rays,"},{"time":505000,"text":"but we didn't even have a viewing box!"},{"time":507000,"text":"And we were doing open-heart surgery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509000,"text":"OK, I know it's not AIDS, I know it's not malaria,"},{"time":511000,"text":"but we still need this stuff. Oh yeah, echo --"},{"time":515000,"text":"this was just to get the children ready and the adults ready."},{"time":519000,"text":"People still believe in Voodoo. Heart disease,"},{"time":522000,"text":"VSD, hole in the heart, tetralogies."},{"time":526000,"text":"You still get people who believe in it and they came."},{"time":529000,"text":"At 67 percent oxygen saturation, the normal is about 97."},{"time":534000,"text":"Her condition, open-heart surgery that as she required,"},{"time":537000,"text":"would have been treated when she was a child."},{"time":540000,"text":"We had to do these for adults. So, we did succeed and we still do."},{"time":544000,"text":"We've done three. We're planning another one in July"},{"time":547000,"text":"in the north of the country. So, we certainly still do open-heart,"},{"time":551000,"text":"but you can see the contrast between everything that was shipped in --"},{"time":556000,"text":"we ship everything, instruments. We had explosions"},{"time":560000,"text":"because the kit was designed and installed by people who weren't used to it."},{"time":567000,"text":"The oxygen tanks didn't quite work right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569000,"text":"But how many did we do the first one? 12."},{"time":573000,"text":"We did 12 open-heart surgical patients successfully."},{"time":577000,"text":"Here is our very first patient, out of intensive care,"},{"time":581000,"text":"and just watch that chair, all right?"},{"time":584000,"text":"This is what I mean about appropriate technology."},{"time":588000,"text":"That's what he was doing, propping up the bed because the bed simply didn't work."},{"time":594000,"text":"Have you seen one of those before?"},{"time":597000,"text":"No? Yes? Doesn't matter, it worked."},{"time":600000,"text":"I'm sure you've all seen or heard this before:"},{"time":602000,"text":"\"We, the willing, have been doing so much with so little for so long --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":607000,"text":"-- we are now qualified to do anything with nothing.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":611000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":614000,"text":"Thank you. Sustainable Solutions -- this was my first company."},{"time":619000,"text":"This one's sole aim is to provide the very things that I think are missing."},{"time":624000,"text":"So, we put my hand in my pocket and say, \"Guys, let's just buy stuff."},{"time":628000,"text":"Let's go set up a company that teaches people, educates them,"},{"time":632000,"text":"gives them the tools they need to keep going.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":635000,"text":"And that's a perfect example of one."},{"time":637000,"text":"Usually when you buy a ventilator in a hospital,"},{"time":639000,"text":"you buy a different one for children,"},{"time":642000,"text":"you buy a different one for transport. This one will do everything,"},{"time":645000,"text":"and it will do it at half the price and doesn't need compressed air."},{"time":647000,"text":"If you're in America and you don't know about this one, we do,"},{"time":650000,"text":"because we make it our duty to find out"},{"time":653000,"text":"what's appropriate technology for Africa -- what's appropriately priced,"},{"time":658000,"text":"does the job, and we move on. Anesthesia machine:"},{"time":662000,"text":"multi-parameter monitor, operating lights, suction."},{"time":665000,"text":"This little unit here -- remember your little 12-volt plug in the car,"},{"time":669000,"text":"that charges your, whatever, Game Boy, telephone?"},{"time":673000,"text":"That's exactly how the outlets are designed."},{"time":676000,"text":"Yes, it will take a solar panel. Yes a solar panel will charge it."},{"time":680000,"text":"But if you've got mains as well, it will charge the batteries in there."},{"time":685000,"text":"And guess what? We have a little pedal charger too, just in case."},{"time":689000,"text":"And guess what, if it all fails,"},{"time":691000,"text":"if you can find a car that's still got a live battery"},{"time":694000,"text":"and you stick it in, it will still work. Then you can customize it."},{"time":699000,"text":"Is it dental surgery you want? General surgery you want?"},{"time":702000,"text":"Decide which instruments, stock it up with consumables."}]},{"cues":[{"time":708000,"text":"And currently we're working on oxygen -- oxygen delivery on-site."},{"time":717000,"text":"The technology for oxygen delivery is not new."},{"time":726000,"text":"Oxygen concentrators are very old technology. What is new,"},{"time":731000,"text":"and what we will have in a few months, I hope,"},{"time":733000,"text":"is that ability to use this same renewable energy system"},{"time":736000,"text":"to provide and produce oxygen on site. Zeolite -- it's not new --"},{"time":743000,"text":"zeolite removes nitrogen from air and nitrogen is 78 percent of air."},{"time":750000,"text":"If you take nitrogen out, what's left? Oxygen, pretty much."},{"time":755000,"text":"So that's not new. What we're doing is applying this technology to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":759000,"text":"These are the basic features of my device, or our device."},{"time":763000,"text":"This is what makes it so special."},{"time":765000,"text":"Apart from the awards it's won,"},{"time":767000,"text":"it's portable and it's certified. It's registered, the MHRA --"},{"time":771000,"text":"and the CE mark, for those who don't know, for Europe, is the equivalent"},{"time":774000,"text":"of the FDA in the U.S."},{"time":778000,"text":"If you compare it with what's on the market, price-wise,"},{"time":782000,"text":"size-wise, ease of use, complexity ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"This picture was taken last year."},{"time":789000,"text":"These are members of my graduating class, 1986."},{"time":793000,"text":"It was in this gentleman's house in the Potomac,"},{"time":795000,"text":"for those of you who are familiar with Maryland."},{"time":799000,"text":"There are too many of us outside and everybody,"},{"time":803000,"text":"just to borrow a bit from Hans -- Hans Rosling, he's my guy --"},{"time":809000,"text":"if the size of the text represents what gets the most attention,"},{"time":814000,"text":"it's the problems. But what we really need are African solutions"},{"time":819000,"text":"that are appropriate for Africa -- looking at the culture,"},{"time":822000,"text":"looking at the people, looking at how much money they've got."},{"time":826000,"text":"African people, because they will do it with a passion, I hope."},{"time":831000,"text":"And lots and lots of that little bit down there, sacrifice."},{"time":835000,"text":"You have to do it. Africans have to do it,"},{"time":838000,"text":"in conjunction with everyone else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":840000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":842000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}